name: Antilles Maneuver (V)
Lore: 'As their war with the Empire continued, Rebel pilots learned ways to counter standard Imperial tactics such as the Tallon Roll.',
Text: 'For remainder of turn, opponent must first use 1 Force to fire a weapon and opponent''s starship weapon destiny draws are -1. OR During opponent''s deploy phase, deploy a Rebel of ability < 3 (except an admiral) from Reserve Deck aboard your starship; reshuffle.',
